the server of AGCInfoApp create on 2016.7.25
==============================================
2016.7.26 更新接口
1、用户注册 prometheus/user/register
请求方式 POST
参数
{
  "username":"",
  "password":"",
  "mobile":""
}
返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "userId": 1,
  "token": "47650c4f4489053d5cfba9ab51514ba2a50e52ed"
}

2、登录 prometheus/user/login
请求方式 POST
参数
{
  "login":"test",
  "password":"123456"
}

返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "userId": 1,
  "token": "47650c4f4489053d5cfba9ab51514ba2a50e52ed"
}

3、获得用户信息 prometheus/user/getInfo?userId=1&token=47650c4f4489053d5cfba9ab51514ba2a50e52ed
请求方式 GET
返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "nickname": "",
    "mobile": "13520358713",
    "email": "",
    "username": "test",
    "sex": "",
    "birthday": 0,
    "pic": "",
    "readNum": 0,
    "commentNum": 0,
    "leval": 1,
    "preference": "",
    "signature":""
  }
}


4、编辑信息 prometheus/user/editInfo
请求方式 POST
参数
{
    "userId": 1,
    "token":"asdffg",
    "nickname": "",
    "mobile": "13520358713",
    "email": "wangchunze@126.com",
    "username": "test",
    "sex": "男",
    "birthday": 0,
    "pic": "",
    "signature":""
}

返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok"
}


5、关注别人 prometheus/user/followOther
请求方式 POST
参数
{
    "userId": 1,
    "friendId":2,
    "token":"asdffg"
}

返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok"
}

6、我的关注 prometheus/user/getFriend?userId=1
请求方式 GET
返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "data": [
    {
      "userId": 2,
      "remarkName": "", --备注
      "nickname": "",
      "sex": "",
      "pic": "",
      "level": 1,
      "signature": ""
    }
  ]
}


7、我的粉丝 prometheus/user/getFans?userId=2
请求方式 GET
返回同上

8、查看别人资料 prometheus/user/getOtherInfo?userId=1
请求方式 GET
返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "nickname": "",
    "mobile": "13520358713",
    "email": "wangchunze@126.com",
    "username": "test",
    "sex": "男",
    "birthday": 0,
    "pic": "",
    "readNum": 0,
    "commentNum": 0,
    "level": 1,
    "preference": "",
    "signature": ""
  }
}

9、搜索人 prometheus/user/searchUser?searchKey=1
GET
返回
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "data": [
    {
      "userId": 1,
      "nickname": "你大爷",
      "sex": "男",
      "pic": ""
    }
  ]
}

==========动态相关接口===========
1、创建动态 /prometheus/moment/createMoment
POST
{
    "userId":1,
    "token":"",
    "newsId":0, --字段可选 不创建该项时为0 或者不传该字段
    "message":"我的动态", --字段可选 不创建该项时为"" 或者不传该字段
    "pics":["aaa.png","bbb.png"] --字段可选 不创建该项时为[""] 或者不传该字段
}

2、动态列表 prometheus/moment/listMoment
GET
{
  "errCode": 0,
  "msg": "ok",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 30,
      "userid": 1,
      "userName": "你大爷",
      "userPic": "",  --用户头像
      "newsId": 0,    --新闻id
      "newsTitle": "", --新闻标题
      "newsPic": "",   --新闻图片
      "newsDesc": "aaa.png#bbb.png", --新闻描述
      "message": "",  --发表的内容
      "createTime": 1469811167457, --时间
      "vote": [
        {
      "userId"->2,
      "userName"->"",
      "userPic"->""
        }
      ],  --点赞
      "comment": [
      {
        "userId"->2,
        "userName"->"",
        "userPic"->"",
        "content"->"", -- 评论内容
        "reId"->""  --回复给某人 被回复人的id
      }
      ]  --评论
    }
  ]
}
































